# Design System

Read `DESIGN.md` before any UI change. Color tokens live in `theme.css`.

## Quick reference

- Background: `--paper` / `--card`
- Text: `--ink` / `--muted`
- Accent: `--accent` (amber) — the only chromatic brand color
- Radius: `--radius` (2px) — do not increase globally
- Mono for keys, codes, timestamps

## Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `theme.css` | Tokens, nav, buttons, panels |
| `styles.css` | Dashboard layout |
| `key.css` | Key management page |
| `DESIGN.md` | Full design contract |
| `vendor/no-slop-ui/` | Anti-AI-slop rules |

When unsure, match existing pages (`index.html`, `keys.html`) rather than generating new patterns.
